SUMMARY:[Standard] Standard Showdown Standard Showdown
LOCATION:Runehammer Games\, 109 Ginn St. \, Tylertown\, MS\, 39667\, US
DESCRIPTION:Format: Standard\nCost: $12\nStore Website: http://www.runeham
 mer.online\nStore Details: https://www.spicerack.gg/events/stores/11455\nE
 vent Details: https://www.spicerack.gg/events/2903672\n\nStandard Showdown
  is a weekly event in Magic: The Gathering that encourages local communiti
 es to engage in Standard format competitions\, offering players a chance t
 o win exclusive promotional cards and prizes.\nOverview of Standard Showdo
 wn\nPurpose: Standard Showdown events are designed to grow local Standard 
 communities and provide a reliable setting for players to compete in the S
 tandard format. These events are typically held weekly at local game store
 s and are open to players of all skill levels. \nFormat: Players bring the
 ir best Standard decks (60-card format) to compete against each other. The
  events usually require a minimum of eight players and consist of at least
  three rounds of play. \nSource: spicerack
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.spicerack.gg/events/2903672
END:VEVENT
